{"id":607002,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【cdtv】别急着掌声雷动-李克强的讲话原来还有下半/","date":"2019-03-06T06:23:05Z","modified":"2019-03-06T06:24:39Z","title":"【CDTV】别急着掌声雷动 李克强的讲话原来还有下半句","content":"<p>3月5日，国务院总理李克强在作政府工作报告时说“两年内基本取消全国高速公路省界收费站，实现不停车快捷收费，减少拥堵、便利群众。”然而在讲话中他在“取消全国高速公路省界收费站”处进行了简短断句，让现场人士误以为是“彻底取消收费站”而响起掌声，未料李克强立刻说出了下半句“实现不停车快捷收费”&#8230;&#8230; 原来只是换种方式高速收费。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"467\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wZFrJodqTtM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-607003\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2f8hj309y0gkaic.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"358\" height=\"596\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2f8hj309y0gkaic.jpg 358w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2f8hj309y0gkaic-180x300.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-607004\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2zsej309t0fpqaa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"353\" height=\"565\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2zsej309t0fpqaa.jpg 353w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2k2zsej309t0fpqaa-187x300.jpg 187w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-607005\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2kg9rqj309t0gnk0h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"353\" height=\"599\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2kg9rqj309t0gnk0h.jpg 353w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/006txUlEly1g0sw2kg9rqj309t0gnk0h-177x300.jpg 177w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" /></p>\n","author":1061,"categories":[18271,18270,1